titles: A briefe discourse, concerning the power of the Peeres, and Commons of Parliament, in point of judicature written by a learned antiquerie, at the request of a peere, of this realme.
author: Selden, John, 1584-1654.
date: printed in the yeere, that sea-coale was exceeding deare, 1640.
